00:00:06.125 --> 00:00:08.650
As soon as you start any work in any place,

00:00:08.650 --> 00:00:13.960
first of all they want Me to cure
people and to help them with curatives.

00:00:13.960 --> 00:00:21.010
Now if I pay attention more to that, then the
main work is to create doctors out of everyone.

00:00:21.010 --> 00:00:22.360
That is neglected.

00:00:22.360 --> 00:00:23.710
Then you become unpopular.

00:00:23.710 --> 00:00:26.800
They think, “Oh, She is not
sympathetic” and this and that.

00:00:26.800 --> 00:00:29.830
But now as we have, everybody
can cure now, everyone.

00:00:29.830 --> 00:00:31.060
I don’t cure anyone directly.

00:00:31.060 --> 00:00:32.830
But they don’t like it.

00:00:32.830 --> 00:00:36.760
They want I should be there and their ego to
be pampered and all those things are there.

00:00:36.760 --> 00:00:38.557
Rather difficult.

00:00:38.557 --> 00:00:41.050
It’s not, we are not running an election, you see,

00:00:41.050 --> 00:00:43.990
like we should please others
sort of thing, is not there.

00:00:43.990 --> 00:00:51.730
But whatever is reality, if a person has
intelligence – pure intelligence – he can

00:00:51.730 --> 00:00:58.930
see that this is something very different and
for that one has to understand that you cannot,

00:00:58.930 --> 00:01:06.220
you cannot force on anyone that
“You get your Realization”.

00:01:06.220 --> 00:01:10.270
In the same way you cannot force
Me that I give you Realization,

00:01:10.270 --> 00:01:12.520
because if it does not work, it does not work.

00:01:12.520 --> 00:01:13.720
It’s such a living force, you see.

00:01:13.720 --> 00:01:16.660
And that upsets them very soon.

00:01:17.673 --> 00:01:25.023
I feel that the way this industrial
revolution has come in the west,

00:01:25.023 --> 00:01:27.940
people have lost their moorings, perhaps.

00:01:27.940 --> 00:01:29.392
They are so confused.

00:01:29.392 --> 00:01:32.980
With all these gurus coming
down here confusing them and

00:01:32.980 --> 00:01:37.338
all kinds of new things coming,
they don’t know where to look.

00:01:37.338 --> 00:01:41.799
But unless and until you get
your evolution completed,

00:01:41.799 --> 00:01:46.570
unless and until you reach that absolute
state of understanding, the chaos will remain.

00:01:46.570 --> 00:01:49.390
So one has to try to get to that.

00:01:49.390 --> 00:01:52.638
But one must understand you can’t pay for it.

00:01:52.638 --> 00:01:54.179
There is no effort.
